{
  "number": 2088,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2088",
  "title": "Add a guide on opensearch",
  "body": "OpenSearch provides search for websites from the url bar, you may have been using it without noticing it, works pretty well.\r\n\r\nWe should add a guide on opensearch in our community websites to show people what can be done when using instantsearch.js/react-instantsearch for OpenSearch.\r\n\r\nIf opensearch is a good pattern that would benefit our users, then we should have a guide about it.\r\n\r\nExample: Try in your browser: \"yarn [TAB] lodash\", this is opensearch. https://github.com/yarnpkg/website/blob/master/opensearch.xml\r\n\r\nIt needs to be linked in the `head` like this:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/yarnpkg/website/blob/66acf52e8f096bef1d74dce6895874f64b3f44d4/_layouts/default.html#L22",
